objectToXMLString

public java.lang.String objectToXMLString(java.lang.Object obj)
Description copied from class: XMLTranslator
Converts an object to a string of XML. The object is converted to a JDOM Document by XMLTranslator.objectToDocument(Object) and then to a string by XMLTranslator.documentToXMLString(org.jdom.Document).
